      "blocks": {
        "template--21507361800487__55bd100e-3bbd-426c-a5cf-eed7b2a3706f-column-1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "\"Finally sleeping through the night\"",
            "text": "<p>I've had insomnia for 6 years. Tried melatonin, apps, everything. The LunaCore mask is the only thing that has actually made a consistent difference. I fall asleep faster and I stay asleep. Genuinely life-changing.</p>",
            "author": "<em><strong>— Anna L., verified buyer</strong></em>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__55bd100e-3bbd-426c-a5cf-eed7b2a3706f-column-2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "\"My nighttime anxiety is gone\"",
            "text": "<p>I used to lie awake for hours with my thoughts racing. Now I'm asleep within 10 minutes. The weight is so calming — it just works. The cooling fabric is a huge bonus too. No more waking up sweaty.</p>",
            "author": "<em><strong>— Maria S., verified buyer</strong></em>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__55bd100e-3bbd-426c-a5cf-eed7b2a3706f-column-3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "\"Best purchase I've made all year\"",
            "text": "<p>Got the Friends Pack for me and my sister. We both absolutely love it. The blackout is incredible — total darkness even on bright mornings. I only wish I'd found this sooner. Worth every cent.</p>",
            "author": "<em><strong>— Sophie K., verified buyer</strong></em>"
          }
        }
      },
